               "text": "### Images from Research Gate\n\nThese images are copyright for Research Gate and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 1</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img9\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img9', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Representation of baboon bone adorned with markings. This image, credited to Enrique Silván Pobes, is featured in the scholarly work of Francisco A. Gonzáles Redondo et al.<br />The original is available in ResearchNet (<htcite0>), and its inclusion here is made possible by the authorization of Doctor Francisco A. Gonzales Redondo.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Beyond fingers (<a href=\"index.html?page=first_steps\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('first_steps','html', '', false); return false;\">First Steps (Volume 1)</a>)</li><li>The Writing System (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>Drawing to count (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>Translation game (Part I)` (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>Together we are strong (Universe)</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
